2013年6月26日，[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|威根竞技]]簽入自由身的麥肯，合約為期三年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/23073721 |title=Burnley midfielder Chris McCann to join Wigan on a free transfer |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-06-26 |accessdate=2015-04-08 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924192957/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/23073721 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 國家隊 ===
麥肯曾代表愛爾蘭在U17、U18及U19的年齡級別參加青少年國際賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10413~34036,00.html |title=International recognition |publisher=[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|''burnleyfootballclub.com'']] |accessdate=2010-07-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100219165701/http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/ProfilesDetail/0%2C%2C10413~34036%2C00.html |archivedate=2010-02-19 }}</ref>。2007年獲[[愛爾蘭21歲以下國家足球隊|愛爾蘭U21]]首次徵召，備戰11月16日及20日對[[黑山21歲以下國家足球隊|黑山]]及[[保加利亞21歲以下國家足球隊|保加利亞]]兩場[[2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]外圍賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.fai.ie/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=2600 |title=Three newcomers included in Ireland’s U21 squad for UEFA Championship matches |publisher=[[愛爾蘭足球協會|''fai.ie'']] |date=2007-11-06 |accessdate=2010-07-19 |archive-date=2018-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181201093319/https://www.fai.ie/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=2600 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他原本入選作客對黑山的賽事，但稱傷沒有上陣，雖然他曾因[[鼠蹊部|腹股溝]]受傷而缺席3場般尼的賽事，卻於對黑山賽前兩天在與[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]的[[同城德比|打吡大戰]]上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.burnley.vitalfootball.co.uk/article.asp?a=104232 |title=McCann No Go Montenegro |publisher=''vitalfootball.co.uk'' |date=2008-03-24 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110911120824/http://www.burnley.vitalfootball.co.uk/article.asp?a=104232 |archive-date=2011-09-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>；返回主場對保加利亞，麥肯於開賽前兩小時向時任領隊[[唐·基雲斯|唐·基雲斯]]（Don Givens）表示不想擔任板凳球員，因而被勒令即時離隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7105449.stm |title=Givens questions McCann's future |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2007-11-21 |accessdate=2011-10-14 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310090347/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7105449.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

